this is the roadmap which you have to follow after installing the repo

1)npm i
2)npm install prisma --save-dev
3)npx prisma init ( if you have a prisma file already then dont run this command)
4)npm install knex
5)npm install pg
6)npm install @prisma/client
7)npx prisma generate (run after making any change in the schema)
8)npx prisma migrate dev --name update_schema (not required initially)
